text: Daria Andreyevna Vaskina (; born 30 July 2002) is a Russian swimmer. She competed in the women's 100 metre backstroke at the 2019 World Aquatics Championships. ==References== Category:2002 births Category:Living people Category:Russian female swimmers Category:Russian female backstroke swimmers Category:Swimmers at the 2018 Summer Youth Olympics Category:Youth Olympic gold medalists for Russia Category:Swimmers from Moscow Category:World Aquatics Championships medalists in swimming
